import React from 'react'
import { Work, Wrapper, WorkContainer, WorkCard } from '../Components/MyWork/MyWork.elements'
import { PageTitle } from '../GlobalStyles'

function MyWork() {
  return (
    <Work id="MyWork">
      <Wrapper>
        <PageTitle>My Work</PageTitle>
        <WorkContainer>
          <WorkCard/>
          <WorkCard/>
          <WorkCard/>
          <WorkCard/>
          <WorkCard/>
          <WorkCard/>
        </WorkContainer>
      </Wrapper>
    </Work>
  )
}

export default MyWork
